B.a35=new A.br("Yaw goal tolerans\u0131",'Arac\u0131n goal yaw\'\u0131ndan bu kadar farkl\u0131 olabilir, h\xe2l\xe2 "ula\u015ft\u0131" say\u0131l\u0131r. Ackermann robot in-place d\xf6nemedi\u011finden tight (<5\xb0) genelde imkans\u0131z \u2192 oscillation. 0.10-0.15 rad (~6-9\xb0) pratik.',"\u2193 tighter yaw ama oscillation, \u2191 rahat oturma","rad",0.05,0.2,"Goal Tolerance")
